  <div class="container">
    <div class="liquid-header text-center">
      <h3 class="blog_heading_style" style="font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 2px;">
        <span>LATEST BLOG</span>
      </h3>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <article class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
          <div class="blog_item">
            <div class="blog_item_image">
              <a href="">
                <img class="lazy" src="//globo-toro.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/img-14-570x280_570x_crop_center.progressive.jpg" alt="Mix &amp; Match - Fall Neutrals" style="display: inline-block;">
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="blog_item_infor">
              <h3 class="blog_item_title"><a href="">Mix &amp; Match - Fall Neutrals</a></h3>
              <div class="blog_author">
                <span>by Globo.io, </span><span class="posted-on"><time datetime="2023-03-01T07:52:00Z">March 01, 2023</time></span>
              </div>
              <div class="blog_item_description">
                All the rumors have finally died down and many skeptics have tightened their lips, the iPod does support video format now on…
              </div>
              <a href="" class="blog_item_btn">Read more</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      	
        <article class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
          <div class="blog_item">
            
            <div class="blog_item_image">
              <a href="">
                <img class="lazy" src="//globo-toro.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/img-13-570x280_570x_crop_center.progressive.jpg" alt="The 5 Things I’m Loving Lately">
              </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="blog_item_infor">
              <h3 class="blog_item_title"><a href="">The 5 Things I’m Loving Lately</a></h3>
              <div class="blog_author">
                <span>by Globo.io, </span><span class="posted-on"><time datetime="2023-03-01T07:52:00Z">March 01, 2023</time></span>
              </div>
              <div class="blog_item_description">
                
                All the rumors have finally died down and many skeptics have tightened their lips, the iPod does support video format now on…
                
              </div>
              <a href="" class="blog_item_btn">Read more</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</div>

